    "faq_accordion_KpFrMh": {
      "type": "faq-accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_item_kJtwLa": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is Franky Protein Iced Coffee?",
            "answer": "<p>Franky Instant Protein Iced Coffee is a premium instant coffee blended with ultra-clean whey protein — giving you the energy of real coffee and the benefits of protein in one delicious scoop. It's designed for anyone who wants a smarter way to start their day, fuel their workouts, or simply enjoy a high-protein coffee without the hassle of brewing or blending.</p><p>Each scoop delivers <strong>10g of whey protein concentrate</strong>, <strong>50mg of natural caffeine</strong>, <strong>200mg of L-theanine</strong> for calm and focused energy, <strong>300mg of lion's mane mushroom extract</strong> to support mental clarity, <strong>1,500mg of psyllium husk fiber</strong> to keep you full and support digestion, and a <strong>probiotic blend (3 million CFU)</strong> for gut health. Zero sugar, gluten-free, soy-free, and keto-friendly. For best results — and the full 20g protein serving — we recommend two scoops.</p><p>Unlike basic protein coffees that simply mix whey into instant coffee, Franky combines protein with functional ingredients that support weight management, gut health, and sustained focus — all in one formula. No protein aftertaste. No artificial fillers. Just real coffee that actually works for your body.</p><p>Preparing it takes under 60 seconds: add one or two scoops to cold water or your milk of choice, stir or shake, and enjoy over ice. We recommend almond milk or regular milk for the best flavor experience — no blender, no barista, no complicated prep required.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_FnK3tU": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What ingredients do you use?",
            "answer": "<p>Our protein coffee is made with high-quality, carefully selected ingredients including Whey Protein Concentrate, real spray dried coffee, Psyllium Husk Powder (1,500 mg), Lion's Mane Mushroom Extract (300 mg), L-Theanine (200 mg), Caffeine Anhydrous (50 mg), and a Probiotic Blend (3 million CFU). It's sweetened naturally with Monk Fruit Extract and Fermented Reb M — no sugar, no artificial sweeteners. Each serving is just 67 calories with 10g of protein. All Franky Nutrition products are proudly made in the USA, 100% gluten-free, and non-GMO.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_p6JKzb": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where are your products manufactured?",
            "answer": "<p>We work exclusively with US-based manufacturers that follow strict quality control standards. All products undergo third-party lab testing to ensure purity, potency, and safety.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_item_kEt6g4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is NOT in Franky Protein Coffee?",
            "answer": "<p>Let's be frank: what we leave out matters just as much as what we put in.</p><p><strong>No Sugar. No Fillers. No Compromises.</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Sugar:</strong> 0g per serving. Period.</li><li><strong>Sucrose:</strong> No table sugar hiding under a different name.</li><li><strong>Stevia:</strong> We use Monk Fruit Extract and Fermented Reb M instead, for a cleaner, smoother sweetness with zero bitter aftertaste.</li><li><strong>Dextrose & Maltodextrin:</strong> No cheap filler carbs that spike your blood sugar.</li><li><strong>Corn Syrup or High-Fructose Corn Syrup:</strong> None. Not even a trace.</li><li><strong>Seed Oils:</strong> No canola, soybean, sunflower, or other inflammatory oils.</li><li><strong>Artificial Sweeteners:</strong> No aspartame, sucralose, or acesulfame-K.</li><li><strong>Artificial Colors or Flavors:</strong> Nothing synthetic. Ever.</li><li><strong>Fillers or Proprietary Blends:</strong> Every ingredient is listed with its exact dose. No mystery formulas, no hidden shortcuts.</li><li><strong>Gluten:</strong> 100% gluten-free.</li><li><strong>Soy:</strong> Completely soy-free.</li><li><strong>GMOs:</strong> Non-GMO verified.</li><li><strong>Pesticides:</strong> Made with organically grown ingredients.</li><li><strong>Heavy Metals:</strong> Every batch is third-party lab tested for purity and safety.</li></ul><p></p><p>You deserve to know exactly what you're putting in your body: and exactly what you're not. That's why our label is fully transparent and our formula stays clean, always.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
