            "answer": "<p>We currently only ship within the United States, but we are planning to expand internationally soon. If you're located outside the US and would like to place an order, feel free to reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:support@frankynu.com\">support@frankynu.com</a> — we'll do our best to help.</p>"
          }
        }
