            "answer": "<p>We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, Diners Club, JCB, Shop Pay, Apple Pay, and Google Pay, PayPal, Venmo and Amazon Pay. All payments are processed securely through Shopify Payments.</p>"
